column5: How was the ice fishing in Minaki ? Where abouts is your cabin ? On the river or one of the lakes ? Ours is on Big Sand, across from Green Island. Yah, that big one with all the windows.....On the map, it's called Martins Beach.Good FishenRob
I'm back, fishing was good lots of fish but not any big onesour cabin is in town on Front Street just down from the store. I'll be going back this weekend I hope. Talk to you later...
